Film4.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
Film4.uk.description: (2015) Part five of the Tom Cruise action-thriller franchise. The secret agents must bring down a terrorist group, but that's not easy when the CIA are hunting you down...

Film4.uk.title: A Most Wanted Man
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Thriller with Philip Seymour Hoffman. The arrival of a refugee in Hamburg sparks a flurry of intelligence activity. Is he an asylum seeker or a terrorist? Strong language/violence.

Film4.uk.title: Like a Boss
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Comedy with Tiffany Haddish and Rose Byrne. When two best friends find their beauty business in dire financial difficulty, they turn to a scary CEO for help.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: The Bedford Incident
Film4.uk.description: (1965) Thriller. Sidney Poitier plays a photojournalist aboard a destroyer whose commander's obsessive hunt for a Soviet sub could plunge the world into nuclear war.

Film4.uk.title: Broken Arrow
Film4.uk.description: (1950) Western starring James Stewart. A gold prospector, tired of reprisal killings between whites and Native Americans, offers a truce to the Apaches' leader. But tensions resurface.

Film4.uk.title: Ten Tall Men
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Comedy adventure. Burt Lancaster stars as a Foreign Legion sergeant leading nine men on a dangerous mission to prevent a Berber attack on a North African desert fort.

Film4.uk.title: Von Ryan's Express
Film4.uk.description: (1965) Second World War adventure. Frank Sinatra stars as the leader of Allied prisoners of war attempting to slip the clutches of their Italian captors. Co-starring Trevor Howard.

Film4.uk.title: The Old Man and the Gun
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Crime biopic. Robert Redford stars as charming 74-year-old robber Forrest Tucker. He's still robbing banks when he falls for farmer Jewel (Sissy Spacek). But the cops still want him.

Film4.uk.title: Heat
Film4.uk.description: (1995) Al Pacino and Robert De Niro star in Michael Mann's crime thriller. A cop sets out to track down a career criminal and his gang of armed robbers. Violence/strong language.

Film4.uk.title: Bad Times at the El Royale
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Crime thriller with Jeff Bridges, Jon Hamm, Dakota Johnson and Chris Hemsworth. Shifty strangers collide in a sleazy-but-glamorous deserted motel with its own buried secrets.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: The Black Shield of Falworth
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Medieval action-adventure starring Tony Curtis and Janet Leigh. When a peasant discovers his true lineage, he sets out to woo his noble sweetheart and avenge his father's murder.

Film4.uk.title: The Spoilers
Film4.uk.description: (1955) Western. Anne Baxter, Jeff Chandler and Rory Calhoun star in a tale of fortune-seeking and treachery on the untamed Alaskan frontier.

Film4.uk.title: The Bravados
Film4.uk.description: (1958) Brooding western starring Joan Collins and Gregory Peck. A man hunts down the four escaped prisoners who he believes are responsible for the murder of his wife.

Film4.uk.title: Film4 Interview Programmes:...
Film4.uk.description: ...Talking Film: Stars and directors talk about the experience of making movies in this compendium of personal and practical reflections.

Film4.uk.title: The Enemy Below
Film4.uk.description: (1957) Second World War thriller. Robert Mitchum stars as the captain of a US destroyer in the North Atlantic hunting down a German U-boat and its world-weary captain, Curt Jurgens.

Film4.uk.title: I, Robot
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Sci-fi thriller with Will Smith. In 2035, a technophobic cop investigates a crime that may have been perpetrated by a robot. Can he keep an open mind?

Film4.uk.title: Commando
Film4.uk.description: (1985) Thriller starring Arnold Schwarzenegger. To free his kidnapped daughter, an ex US commando must agree to assassinate a South American president. But he's not as pliant as he seems...

Film4.uk.title: The Last Stand
Film4.uk.description: (2013) Thriller starring Arnold Schwarzenegger, Johnny Knoxville and Forest Whitaker. A small-town sheriff and his inexperienced staff take on a drug cartel boss who's fleeing to Mexico.

Film4.uk.title: How to Build a Girl
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Caitlin Moran's coming-of-age comedy based on her own experiences of trying to make it as a music journo in London. Cool people are the worst. Strong language/sex/self-harm.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: How Green Was My Valley
Film4.uk.description: (1941) Walter Pidgeon, Maureen O'Hara and Roddy McDowall star in John Ford's multi-Oscar-winning period drama set in the mining communities of the South Wales Valleys of the 19th century.

Film4.uk.title: Mary, Queen of Scots
Film4.uk.description: (1971) Vanessa Redgrave stars in a dramatisation of the life of the 16th-century Scottish queen. Glenda Jackson co-stars as her cousin and rival, England's Queen Elizabeth I. Violence.

Film4.uk.title: Anzio
Film4.uk.description: (1968) Epic Second World War drama starring Robert Mitchum. A reporter gets trapped behind enemy lines during the costly 1944 Allied invasion of Italy. With Peter Falk and Robert Ryan.

Film4.uk.title: Film4 Interview Programmes:...

Film4.uk.title: A Knight's Tale
Film4.uk.description: (2001) Modern swashbuckling medieval action adventure starring Heath Ledger, Shannyn Sossamon and Paul Bettany. A lowly squire jousts his way to the top, with help from Geoffrey Chaucer.

Film4.uk.title: The Equalizer 2
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Action crime thriller sequel. Denzel Washington returns as Robert McCall, who's out for revenge after ruthless killers murder an agency contact who he also considered a friend.

Film4.uk.title: The Straight Story
Film4.uk.description: (1999) David Lynch's fact-based drama with Richard Farnsworth. Alvin Straight drives hundreds of miles across the USA on a lawnmower to visit his dying brother - Harry Dean Stanton.
